---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About | Kenah Field">
  <main class="py-20">
    <article class="prose prose-invert mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl text-heading-blue">About Kenah</h1>

      <p class="lead">
        This is the space to introduce yourself. Talk about your journey as an actor, artist, and bodyworker, and how those paths intersect.
      </p>

      <img 
  src="/images/kenah.png" 
  alt="A photo of Kenah" 
  class="w-full max-w-sm mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg my-12"
>

      <h2>My Philosophy</h2>
      <p>
        Here, you can expand on the ideas in your Manifesto. What drives your work? What is the core ethos of "Kenah Field"? This is where you build a deeper connection with your audience.
      </p>

      <h2>My Work</h2>
      <p>
        You can briefly describe your different practices here, with links to the relevant sections of your site or your other platforms.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><a href="/portfolio">Explore my creative portfolio</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services">Learn about my bodywork practice</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://kenahfield.com" target="_blank">Wander through my digital garden</a></li>
      </ul>

    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>